metadata.name: Galactic Visions #1 2023
metadata.description:
A Surreal Journey Through the Cosmos

"The cosmos is a vast, surreal landscape, full of mysteries and wonders waiting to be explored. It is a journey that will take us to the far reaches of the universe and beyond, a journey that will challenge us, inspire us, and ultimately, transform us. So let us embrace the journey and embrace the unknown, for in doing so, we open ourselves up to a world of endless possibility and boundless potential."

#1 of 2023
